      <title>冰岛投资者托马斯多蒂尔接近总统大选胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/iceland-s-presidential-race-sees-investor-tomasdottir-in-lead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冰岛企业家兼投资者哈拉·托马斯多蒂尔 (Halla Tomasdottir) 有望在总统选举中获胜，前总理卡特琳·雅各布斯多蒂尔 (Katrin Jakobsdottir) 落后。]]></description>
